text: Jiang Chunli (born 2 March 1981) is a Chinese cross-country skier. She competed in two events at the 2006 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female cross- country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of China Category:Cross- country skiers at the 2006 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
